    "Therefore, comprehensive lifecycle management (LCM) of virtualized heterogeneous hardware in a cloud-native manner must be implemented to cater to the various demands of AI applications.",
    "This cloud-based LCM scheme may encompass the following processes.",
    "Resource discovery: it involves identifying the characteristics and capabilities of each virtualized hardware resource within the cloud infrastructure.",
    "Configuration: virtualized hardware resources must be configured based on requirements.",
    "For GPUs, configuration parameters may include driver types, partitioning methods, memory allocation methods, and specialized features."
